Upload custom-emails folder to wp-content/uploads folder and edit class-tracking-number-email.php and email-functions.php as needed.
Upload tracking-email.php to wp-content/plugins/woocommerce/templates/emails and edit the email template as needed
Copy wordpress_fuctions.php content to your wordpress theme functions.php and read the comments


 The process to this mail being triggered is the following:
-Create email class and a conditional check to a custom field value
-Create a new "Shipped" order status and automatically set order status to it when custom field value is set
-Send custom email when order status is on shipped
-Set order status back to processing so another integrations can continue handling it


Any updates or improvments are welcome!
